{
  "texts": [
    "In this work, the authors apply a pretrained BERE model to identify microbedisease associations.",
    "BERE is a deep learning model initially developed for extracting drug-related associations (Hong et al., 2020).",
    "The model is pretrained using a biomedical corpus.",
    "The model converts the text into vector representation using word embeddings with sentences represented as 200-dimensional concatenations.",
    "Then the recurrent neural network encodes short-and long-range dependencies, as well as semantic features using gated recurrent units (GRUs)."
  ]
}